    <description>MWD26 admin demo — runs on an Integration Request record page. Calls the Back_Office_Callout subflow to send the record to the Target Org, then updates the record and writes an Integration_Log__c row. No Apex, no hardcoded URL/secret (the subflow uses Named Credential Target_Org_NC).</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>fRequestPayload</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
